data.description:
Sellers have moved out, showing availability has been opened up. 
SELLER’S LOAN IS ASSUMABLE AT 5.75%!!! Water heater has 4 year warranty, and all paperwork regarding work completed is listed in supplements.  
Welcome home to this beautiful property nestled in the highly sought after Widmer Park subdivision!  Equipped with ample space to entertain friends and family this holiday season. This home is waiting for your personal touches; conveniently located near fantastic shops, a wonderful school district, and close highway access.  The vaulted ceiling in the great room frames the gorgeous fireplace inviting new memories to be made and shared.  A completely finished basement boasting a non-conforming bedroom and bathroom has space for everyone! Brand new water heater with new duct work was installed last year.  Are you a maker?  The outbuilding listed is amazing!  Originally constructed to fashion boats, this space is the perfect workshop.  Come see for yourself this rare gem in Shawnee!
